channel.title: Preset track name Challenge
channel.description:
When working on a track, we like to have cool, funny, or interesting titles/names for them. But in this challenge, post a track with the name that Auxy gave to your project!
Anything can be used, any genre, Key, BPM!
Only rule is to have the name that the app gave you when you opened the project!
[If enough of you participate I can pout them into a playlist on my soundcloud page]
Thanks :smiley:
